name: onshape-desktop-shell
description: Onshape desktop app (web application shell). Unofficial.

scripts.start: npm install && npm run compile && electron ./app

releases.body:
- Add History submenu to application menu — Back, Forward and Home (https://cad.onshape.com/documents) actions.
- Make app single instance (disallow multiple instances of to run).
- Upgrade to [Electron 0.36.7](https://github.com/atom/electron/releases/tag/v0.36.7).

- Implemented auto update.
- Upgrade to [Electron 0.36.2](https://github.com/atom/electron/releases/tag/v0.36.2).
- Implemented application menu. You can find useful links in the Help menu (Support, Forum, Blog, Status).
- Keep opened windows state (restore last opened documents on launch).

- Implemented auto sign in.
- Upgrade to [Electron 0.36.1](https://github.com/atom/electron/releases/tag/v0.36.1).
